d\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\"></iframe><noscript><iframe src=\"https://anchor.fm/tabletopgamesblog/embed/episodes/Uncertain-death-Topic-Discussion-e1m4v4a\" height=\"102px\" width=\"100%\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></noscript>\r\n<p>Intro Music: <em>Bomber (Sting)</em> by <em>Riot</em> (<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/audiolibrary/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https://www.youtube.com/audiolibrary/</a>)</p>\r\n<p>The following music was used for this media project:<br>Music: Silent Alpha by MusicParadise<br>Free download: https://filmmusic.io/song/5067-silent-alpha<br>License (CC BY 4.0): https://filmmusic.io/standard-license<br>Artist website: http://www.music-paradise.de</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div id=\"jp-relatedposts\" class=\"jp-relatedposts\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n<h3 class=\"jp-relatedposts-headline\"><em>Related</em></h3>\r\n<div class=\"jp-relatedposts-items jp-relatedposts-items-visual jp-relatedposts-grid \"><div class=\"jp-relatedposts-post jp-relatedposts-post0 jp-relatedposts-post-thumbs\" data-post-id=\"12735\" data-post-format=\"false\"><a class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-a\" href=\"/2022/08/02/enough-is-enough-minimum-board-game-review-requirements-topic-discussion/?relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0&amp;relatedposts_hit=1&amp;relatedposts_origin=12796&amp;relatedposts_position=0\" title=\"Enough is enough &amp;#8211; minimum board game review requirements (Topic Discussion)\" data-origin=\"12796\" data-position=\"0\"><img class=\"jp-relatedposts-post-img\" loading=\"lazy\" 